## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all perspectives or the most recent developments in the field of cybersecurity. The dynamic nature of the industry means that new trends and challenges can emerge rapidly, potentially altering the landscape. Additionally, the reliance on English-language sources may limit the inclusion of global perspectives.